# Heavy binary/context-noise files
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.docx
**/*.zip
**/*.pdf

# Orphan UI mockups
src/desktop/Barberia.Desktop/Views/ggg*.html
"@ | Set-Content .codexignore